msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:82
msgid "Centralises all editor state into a single custom hook, providing:"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:84
msgid ""
"State slices for every tab (service, organization, legalResource, "
"temporalRules, parameters, cprmvRules, cost, output, dmnData, "
"iknowMappingConfig)"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:85
msgid "A `clearAllData()` action that resets the entire editor"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:87
msgid ""
"This replaces dozens of individual `useState` calls that were previously "
"spread across `App.js`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:89
msgid "`src/hooks/useArrayHandlers.js`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:91
msgid ""
"Provides DRY CRUD handlers for any array-based state (rules, parameters, "
"CPRMV rules):"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:93
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  handleAdd,        // Append new item with auto-incremented ID\n"
"  handleUpdate,     // Update item by ID with partial patch\n"
"  handleRemove,     // Remove item by ID\n"
"  handleUpdateField,// Update a single field (convenience wrapper)\n"
"  handleClear,      // Clear the entire array\n"
"  handleReplace     // Replace the entire array\n"
"}"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:104
msgid ""
"IDs use `Math.max(...ids) + 1` — stable under rapid additions, unlike "
"`Date.now()`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:106
msgid "`src/utils/ttlGenerator.js`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:108
msgid ""
"Class-based TTL generation. Each tab section has a corresponding generate "
"method. Called by `App.js` on export and by `PreviewPanel` on every state "
"change."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:110
msgid "`src/utils/parseTTL.enhanced.js`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:112
msgid ""
"Full TTL parser. Handles vocabulary detection, multi-line values, namespace "
"resolution, date parsing, array extraction (keywords), and DMN block capture "
"and preservation. Returns a data structure matching the editor state shape "
"for direct use in `useEditorState`."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:114
msgid "`src/config/vocabularies_config.js`"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/cpsv-editor%5Cdeveloper%5Cproject-structure.md:116
msgid ""
"Configuration-driven vocabulary management. Defines namespace-to-prefix "
"mappings, RDF type-to-editor-section mappings, and property aliases. See "
"[Vocabulary Configuration]{1} for how to extend it."
msgstr ""

